body:
UVM has this:

```
task uvm_wait_for_nba_region;
  int nba;
  int next_nba;
  next_nba++;
  //vvvv -- %Error-UNSUPPORTED: t/t_uvm_pkg_todo.vh:875:7: Unsupported: Delayed assignment inside public function/task
  nba <= next_nba;
  @(nba);
endtask
```

This blocks UVM post-elaboration.  Despite the message the function isn't public, it's because it (probably correctly) couldn't inline.
